column1: Contains 'b' box harmonic coefficients for Arridge and Eggington (2022) magnetopause field model of Uranus in nT*R_U
column3: so that each row represents a single i and each column a single k. Unlike spherical harmonics
column4: there are no powers of i or k
column5: so the indices are arbitrary. See https://doi.org/10.1016/j.icarus.2021.114562
